{"tid":877632,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【元朗新盤】朗城滙首推504伙賣不足四成 新例後銷情最差鐵路盤","createTime":"2018-10-26T13:24:08.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-26T15:56:08.000Z","uid":174649,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"82b6ef0fc3450ff4c1e7fce1b3cbde3cd4679c76","tid":877632,"uid":174649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T13:24:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181026/large/1540550840_c245.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181026%2Flarge%2F1540550840_c245.jpg&h=be74df1a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【18:20】消息指，項目今日售出197伙，佔推售量不足4成，成為2013年實施一手新例後，首批銷情最差的港鐵新盤。近年各個港鐵新盤首批皆賣得滿堂紅，全部首日都賣超過9成半以上。資料顯示，同系的荃灣西站全．城滙去年8月開售521伙，即日沽清全數單位。至於對上一個鐵路盤，南豐旗下康城站LP6，首批478伙於9月底開售，即日售出486伙，佔推售量98%。"},{"pid":"edfe05669b6ae672c0e983c05f14a4af5c9c65fc","tid":877632,"uid":4826,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T13:28:07.000Z","msg":"咩新例"},{"pid":"be4c39d2564a2cb3caf48995c8d8623bbbf74725","tid":877632,"uid":171192,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T13:29:20.000Z","msg":"今日空氣差啲人未出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c62d43e069d71be14c1d67851f32fb92aa705438","tid":877632,"uid":153778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T13:31:24.000Z","msg":"元朗閒日唔計"},{"pid":"f4ecc84652c956ba78930f7249692d45b28ecffa","tid":877632,"uid":7369,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T13:35:37.000Z","msg":"其實入三千張票但連504伙都賣唔晒代表咩? 有冇好友解釋下?"},{"pid":"7644e196463a7b21b0f0e2420f0ee55571247023","tid":877632,"uid":56219,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T13:39:06.000Z","msg":"星期5開賣...聽日先發力"},{"pid":"2f10b74343e032302ef9428670f83a300a056729","tid":877632,"uid":6297,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T13:39:49